Employee:

Attributes:

name (String)

baseSalary (double)

id (int) (assigned sequentially)

manager (Employee)

Methods:

Employee(String name, double baseSalary): constructor

double getBaseSalary(): returns base salary

String getName(): returns name

int getEmployeeID(): returns ID

Employee getManager(): returns manager

boolean equals(Employee other): compares two employees

String toString(): returns string representation

String employeeStatus(): returns employee status (abstract)
